2. Added `try { simp_all [Set.mem_Icc] }` to simplify the membership conditions
3. Added `try { contradiction }` to find contradictions in the hypotheses
4. Added `try { omega }` to solve goals involving natural number arithmetic
5. Added `try { aesop }` as a general-purpose solver
6. Kept `try { contradiction }` and `try { omega }` at the end to catch any remaining simple goals

